    "At the same time, it is associated with increased computational demands.",
    "A separate metric of the capability of a LLM is the size of the context window.",
    "It is typically measured in the number of tokens.",
    "Roughly speaking, this is the amount of information (context) in a session that the model can \"remember\" or refer to.",
    "Most LLMs have a context window of a few thousands tokens, but Anthropic's Claude 2 boasts a large context"
